Subject: 500 Internal Server Error
Description:
Hi Support, 

Our customer is experiencing a 500 Internal Server Error when accessing the EPP server. We need your help to remotely resolve this issue.
Please let us know your availability for a remote session today.

Thank you.

Regards,
Solution_Comment__c: Moved the files ib_logfile0 and ib_logfile1 from /var/lib/mysql/, and the Mysql service could start normal after that.
